item.title: I cant vonnect using my ip, i have done the port thing
item.dc:creator: @the1337legend the1337legend
item.description:
@the1337legend wrote:

Client sided - Client> Client.java> Ctrl+f, search “43594” change it to 5555, search it again to make sure it isn’t further down, do the same, change it to 5555.

Server sided - Server> Server.java(or)Server.ini> change ServerPort=43594 to ServerPort=5555
